    <item>
      <title>2-25</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/zh/composition/2-25/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/zh/composition/2-25/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;youtube-embed&#34; style=&#34;max-width:900px; margin: 1.2rem 0;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;iframe width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;250&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/avDgWoLj_Ao&#34; title=&#34;2-25&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A short piece written for recorder quintet, imitating the lively atmosphere of Chinese New Year.&#xA;Blending fantasy and folk-ish styles, it features strong rhythmic patterns and non-functional harmonies to evoke a sense of Eastern mystery and celebration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
